# English Learning Overlay App - Implementation Plan

A Flutter Android app that displays English learning sentences (with Arabic translations) as a floating system overlay at user-defined intervals, similar to Azkar apps. Uses `SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW` instead of notifications.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **No Android device detected.** Only Windows/Chrome/Edge are available. The app will be built and analyzed for errors, but **you will need to build and test the APK on a physical Android device or emulator yourself**. I'll ensure the code compiles cleanly via `flutter analyze`.

> [!NOTE]
> The `flutter_overlay_window` package requires Android-specific native code. The overlay and foreground service functionality **cannot be tested on Windows/Chrome** — only on Android.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Project Scaffold

#### [NEW] Flutter project at `c:\Users\user\Downloads\learn english`
- Create via `flutter create` with package name `com.app.learn_english`
- Android-only target (though Flutter creates multi-platform by default)

#### Dependencies (pubspec.yaml)
| Package | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `flutter_overlay_window` | System overlay display |
| `flutter_tts` | Text-to-speech pronunciation |
| `hive` + `hive_flutter` | Local storage for settings |
| `flutter_riverpod` | State management |
| `google_fonts` | Premium typography |

---

### Data Layer

#### [NEW] `lib/models/sentence.dart`
- `Sentence` class with `id`, `english`, `arabic`, `isLearned` fields

#### [NEW] `assets/sentences.json`
- 50+ English sentences with Arabic translations
- Categories: greetings, daily life, travel, emotions, business

#### [NEW] `lib/core/sentence_repository.dart`
- Load sentences from JSON
- Random selection avoiding consecutive repeats
- Filter out learned sentences
- Daily count tracking

---

### Core Services

#### [NEW] `lib/core/services/overlay_service.dart`
- Wrapper around `flutter_overlay_window`
- Show/close overlay
- Permission request handling
- Prevent multiple overlays stacking

#### [NEW] `lib/core/services/tts_service.dart`
- Wrapper around `flutter_tts`
- Speak English sentence
- Configure voice, speed, pitch

#### [NEW] `lib/core/services/timer_service.dart`
- Periodic timer with configurable interval (5/10/15/30 min)
- Start/stop/reset
- Triggers overlay display

#### [NEW] `lib/core/services/storage_service.dart`
- Hive-based persistence for:
  - Selected interval
  - Service running state
  - Learned sentence IDs
  - Daily display count

---

### State Management (Riverpod)

#### [NEW] `lib/core/providers.dart`
- `settingsProvider` — interval, running state
- `sentenceProvider` — current sentence, history
- `ttsProvider` — TTS service instance
- `overlayProvider` — overlay service instance

---

### Overlay UI

#### [NEW] `lib/features/overlay/overlay_main.dart`
- **Overlay entry point** (registered with `flutter_overlay_window`)
- Separate `main()` for overlay process

#### [NEW] `lib/features/overlay/overlay_widget.dart`
- Glassmorphic card design with:
  - English text (large, bold)
  - Arabic translation (smaller, lighter)
  - Close (X) button
  - Play pronunciation (TTS) button
  - "Mark as learned" button
  - Countdown progress bar (20s auto-dismiss)
  - Fade-in + slide-up animation
  - Swipe to see next sentence
- Draggable via `flutter_overlay_window` config

---

### Main App UI

#### [NEW] `lib/features/settings/settings_screen.dart`
- Premium Material 3 design with gradient background
- Interval selector (custom wheel/dropdown)
- Animated Start/Stop toggle switch
- Permission status indicator
- Daily sentence count display
- Statistics section

#### [NEW] `lib/main.dart`
- App entry point
- Hive initialization
- Material 3 theme with custom color scheme
- Riverpod scope

#### [NEW] `lib/core/theme.dart`
- Custom Material 3 theme
- Color palette (deep purple/indigo gradients)
- Typography via Google Fonts

---

### Android Configuration

#### [MODIFY] `android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml`
- Add `SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW` permission
- Add `FOREGROUND_SERVICE` permission
- Add `RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED` for service restart
- Configure overlay entry point

#### [MODIFY] `android/app/build.gradle`
- Set `minSdkVersion` to 23 (for overlay support)
- Set `compileSdkVersion` to 34

