## Project Structure
```
lib/
├── main.dart                          # App entry point
├── core/
│   ├── theme.dart                     # Material 3 theme
│   ├── providers.dart                 # Riverpod providers
│   ├── sentence_repository.dart       # Sentence data access
│   └── services/
│       ├── overlay_service.dart       # Overlay management
│       ├── tts_service.dart           # Text-to-speech
│       ├── timer_service.dart         # Interval timer
│       └── storage_service.dart       # Hive persistence
├── models/
│   └── sentence.dart                  # Sentence model
└── features/
    ├── overlay/
    │   ├── overlay_main.dart          # Overlay entry point
    │   └── overlay_widget.dart        # Overlay UI
    └── settings/
        └── settings_screen.dart       # Main settings screen
assets/
└── sentences.json                     # Sentence database
```

